description: Copies a job template to an Amazon S3 bucket.

parameters.name: targetS3Location
parameters.description: The Amazon S3 bucket name and key where you would like to add a copy of the job template. The name of the Amazon S3 bucket. The Amazon S3 object key that uniquely identifies the Amazon S3 bucket.

nested_params.name: bucketName
nested_params.description: The name of the Amazon S3 bucket.

nested_params.name: key
nested_params.description: The Amazon S3 object key that uniquely identifies the Amazon S3 bucket.

nested_items.name: templateType
nested_items.description: The format of the job template, either JSON or YAML.
